# Note: test_data/ is NOT excluded here. It is bind-mounted into the build
# stage (see Dockerfile) so that non-test code in src/ can embed fixtures
# (e.g. pebble.pem) via include_bytes!/include_str! at compile time.
# Bind mounts are ephemeral and never persist into the final image, so
# test_data/ does not end up in the production image.
